🧱 Section Skeleton (One-Page Structure)
Hero Section (Video Header)
Full-width autoplay video background (muted, looped)
Overlay text:
Headline: e.g., "Erleben Sie Europa mit uns"
Subheadline: "Komfortable Busreisen & zuverlässige Busvermietung seit Jahrzehnten"
CTA buttons: “Unsere Reisen ansehen” & “Bus mieten”
Optional logo top-left, hamburger menu top-right (mobile-friendly)

Section: Our Trips ("Unsere Reisen")
Tabs or filters: "Tagesfahrten", "Mehrtagestouren", "Musikreisen", "Marktbesuche"
Each trip block includes:
Title, thumbnail, date, duration, price
Short description
“Mehr erfahren” or “Jetzt buchen” button

Section: Bus Rental ("Busvermietung")
Description of available rental options (e.g. for Vereine, Firmen)
Features or benefits grid (e.g., Komfort, Sicherheit, Flexibilität)
Rental inquiry form or CTA: “Jetzt anfragen”

About / Company Section
Brief history + emphasis on years of experience and personalized service
Optional quote/testimonial

Photo of founder/team or buses

Testimonials / Reviews

Carousel or grid of short guest testimonials

Optional Google or Facebook review integration

Contact Section
Address, phone, email
Embedded map

Contact form (simple: name, email, message)

Office hours

Footer

Logo

Mini nav: Impressum, Datenschutz, AGB

Social media icons (if applicable)

Copyright